WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.920
SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:39.320 --> 01:42.960
ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>QUEEN CHU</i> ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:48.480
<i>That day, blood stained the Palace walls.</i>

01:49.960 --> 01:51.160
<i>It showed me the truth.</i>

01:52.280 --> 01:54.720
<i>There's no real love in these halls.</i>

01:55.800 --> 01:58.080
<i>If fate grants me another chance,</i>

01:58.160 --> 02:02.440
<i>I would tell you of every misstep</i>
<i>and how they</i>

02:03.600 --> 02:05.640
<i>led to my ruin.</i>

02:08.639 --> 02:10.400
‎YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

02:28.080 --> 02:29.560
Stop! Stop there!

02:29.640 --> 02:30.960
My horse!

02:33.960 --> 02:35.200
<i>I'm Chu Zhao.</i>

02:35.280 --> 02:38.240
<i>I grew up in Yunzhong,</i>
<i>a desert prefecture.</i>

02:38.320 --> 02:39.560
<i>This is part of the frontier.</i>

02:39.640 --> 02:41.720
<i>Foes from the Northern Desert</i>
<i>often invade.</i>

02:41.800 --> 02:43.240
<i>My mother died when I was little.</i>

02:43.320 --> 02:45.080
<i>I've been living with my father.</i>

02:45.160 --> 02:46.720
<i>He's a frontier general</i>

02:46.800 --> 02:48.840
<i>who has served for over a decade.</i>

02:48.920 --> 02:50.360
<i>My impression of Mother is just</i>

02:50.440 --> 02:53.120
<i>what Father told me in my childhood.</i>

02:53.200 --> 02:54.120
THE CAPITAL

02:54.200 --> 02:57.960
<i>The Capital is where my mother</i>
<i>used to live.</i>

02:58.040 --> 03:00.360
<i>I longed so much to visit it,</i>

03:00.440 --> 03:03.600
<i>but my father forbade me</i>
<i>to leave Yunzhong.</i>

03:03.680 --> 03:05.520
<i>Now, I've grown up.</i>

03:05.600 --> 03:07.080
<i>I can gallop on a horse, too.</i>

03:07.160 --> 03:08.080
He, all alone,

03:08.160 --> 03:09.680
stands against thousands of troops.

03:09.760 --> 03:12.400
That's how he subdued
the Northern Desert all alone!

03:13.000 --> 03:13.880
Brilliant!

03:14.720 --> 03:16.520
Miss. You're so pretty. Want a flower?

03:18.680 --> 03:19.800
One more!

03:20.400 --> 03:21.800
<i>Carriages constantly move.</i>

03:21.880 --> 03:23.000
<i>People walk around.</i>

03:23.800 --> 03:26.280
<i>The city is crowded and bustling.</i>

03:26.920 --> 03:30.080
<i>When the scenes here</i>
<i>became vivid in front of me,</i>

03:30.600 --> 03:32.200
<i>I finally realized something.</i>

03:33.160 --> 03:35.640
<i>How I wish my mother were still alive.</i>

03:37.960 --> 03:40.080
<i>How I wish she could stay by my side,</i>

03:40.680 --> 03:43.640
<i>choosing hairpins</i>
<i>for my coming-of-age ceremony,</i>

03:43.720 --> 03:46.480
<i>and see what I've become.</i>

03:46.560 --> 03:47.520
LOTUS PAVILION

03:49.520 --> 03:50.360
Go fight it!

03:53.000 --> 03:54.280
Go for it!

03:54.920 --> 03:58.280
-Good!
-Do it!

03:59.120 --> 04:00.600
Beat him! Kill him!

04:00.680 --> 04:01.520
-Beat him!
-Excuse me.

04:02.480 --> 04:03.960
Beat him!

04:04.720 --> 04:05.680
Beat hard!

04:24.240 --> 04:26.120
In broad daylight, how can you lynch him?

04:26.200 --> 04:27.840
Who are you, girl? Go away!

04:27.920 --> 04:29.000
He's terrible.

04:29.080 --> 04:32.440
Last night, he burned the Wei Village
and killed 46 people.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.280
Death is too good for him.

04:34.360 --> 04:35.480
Let's kill him.

04:35.560 --> 04:38.640
By law,
lynching is no different from murder.

04:39.320 --> 04:40.960
I've finally found you.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.360
Come on. Be good, will you?

04:42.440 --> 04:43.360
ZHONG CHANGRONG
DEPUTY GENERAL OF FRONTIER TROOPS

04:43.440 --> 04:45.120
-Sorry for this. Sorry.
-Mr. Zhong.

04:45.200 --> 04:47.280
They're killing him casually!

04:47.360 --> 04:48.200
Behave.

04:49.640 --> 04:50.480
Why do you stop me?

04:51.080 --> 04:53.080
-They're in the wrong.
-You…

04:53.160 --> 04:54.320
Without interrogation,

04:54.400 --> 04:56.720
they convicted him
and were trying to lynch him.

04:56.800 --> 04:57.840
Oh, you don't understand.

04:58.520 --> 05:01.600
Just stay out of the intricate affairs
of these big clans.

05:01.680 --> 05:03.440
Your father gave me an order.

05:03.520 --> 05:04.800
I must take you back.

05:04.880 --> 05:05.920
Let's go.

05:09.960 --> 05:12.040
Excuse me. Please let us through.

05:14.240 --> 05:15.440
Leave. Leave now.

05:15.960 --> 05:18.320
-Go away. Mind your own business.
-We can't let him go!

05:18.400 --> 05:20.320
Let's go.

05:20.400 --> 05:22.200
Come on.

05:25.080 --> 05:26.880
<i>Not even a full day in the Chu capital,</i>

05:26.960 --> 05:28.960
<i>Mr. Zhong brought me back to Yunzhong.</i>

05:29.600 --> 05:30.440
<i>Just as I thought,</i>

05:30.520 --> 05:31.360
MILITARY CAMP OF YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

05:31.440 --> 05:33.640
<i>Father was furious that I ran off.</i>

05:33.720 --> 05:36.400
Yunzhong is so far away from the Capital.

05:36.920 --> 05:38.560
Do you know how many bandits

05:38.640 --> 05:39.960
and enemies are out there?

05:40.680 --> 05:42.360
-What if--?
-What?

05:42.440 --> 05:44.800
Am I not standing here safe and sound?

05:44.880 --> 05:47.400
Why do you always want to trap me in here?

05:47.480 --> 05:48.680
CHU LING, THE GUARD GENERAL

05:48.760 --> 05:49.680
When I was in the Capital,

05:50.280 --> 05:52.040
I visited my uncle and my cousin.

05:52.760 --> 05:55.000
I also experienced local customs there.

05:55.080 --> 05:56.440
How ignorant you are!

05:57.080 --> 05:59.200
You only know the Capital
is your mother's hometown.

05:59.280 --> 06:00.840
Do you know it's also a devouring cage?

06:00.920 --> 06:04.120
Father, don't scare me.
I just missed my mother.

06:04.640 --> 06:05.720
I didn't grow up by her side,

06:05.800 --> 06:07.600
so I wanted to take a look.

06:08.280 --> 06:09.400
To look at the sights she saw

06:09.480 --> 06:11.320
and walk the lanes she walked.

06:12.200 --> 06:13.680
I wanted to find

06:13.760 --> 06:16.920
even the slightest trace
of my mother's existence.

06:17.000 --> 06:18.800
How dare you bring her up?

06:19.920 --> 06:22.560
If she knew you were being so willful,

06:22.640 --> 06:24.120
she would be heartbroken!

06:24.200 --> 06:26.240
I just try to live on my own terms.

06:26.320 --> 06:27.760
Does it make me willful?

06:27.840 --> 06:30.120
If Mother were still alive,

06:30.200 --> 06:32.560
she wouldn't want me
to be an obedient girl.

06:33.320 --> 06:35.080
She wouldn't be as arrogant as you.

06:36.040 --> 06:38.160
She would care about my feelings.

06:38.760 --> 06:39.720
Yeah.

06:40.760 --> 06:42.960
You're the undefeated God of War.

06:43.040 --> 06:45.360
You're the esteemed Guard General.

06:45.440 --> 06:48.480
But have you ever asked
if I wish to be a general's daughter?

06:49.640 --> 06:51.000
Since childhood,

06:51.520 --> 06:53.280
other girls have had parents around.

06:53.360 --> 06:54.440
What about me?

06:55.040 --> 06:56.960
I've always been neglected.

06:57.880 --> 07:00.400
Have I ever cried or complained to you?

07:00.480 --> 07:02.600
I've never dared
to ask you for a little concern.

07:02.680 --> 07:03.880
Because you've always been busy.

07:04.800 --> 07:06.280
You're busy protecting frontier people.

07:06.360 --> 07:08.840
You're busy forging your fame.

07:08.920 --> 07:10.160
You're too busy

07:10.240 --> 07:13.240
to ask your daughter
what she really wants!

07:25.280 --> 07:26.320
<i>Lan,</i>

07:27.280 --> 07:28.520
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

07:29.520 --> 07:31.680
<i>I failed to take good care</i>
<i>of our daughter.</i>

07:32.200 --> 07:35.520
<i>All I can do now is grant her wish.</i>

07:40.800 --> 07:44.160
CHU

07:44.240 --> 07:45.880
CHU MANSION

07:45.960 --> 07:49.360
<i>What I said to Father</i>
<i>must have broken his heart.</i>

07:49.440 --> 07:51.720
<i>Otherwise, he wouldn't have sent me</i>

07:51.800 --> 07:53.280
<i>to the Capital as I always wished,</i>

07:53.360 --> 07:55.960
<i>to the Chu Mansion granted by His Majesty.</i>

07:57.000 --> 07:59.360
<i>I tried hard to learn manners,</i>

07:59.440 --> 08:01.400
<i>expecting to be a true noble lady</i>

08:01.480 --> 08:03.720
<i>in the Capital</i>
<i>as my father described my mother.</i>

08:04.440 --> 08:07.520
<i>I'd behave gracefully</i>
<i>and smile with lips closed.</i>

08:09.200 --> 08:12.960
<i>However, these things</i>
<i>were far harder than I ever imagined.</i>

08:15.640 --> 08:17.400
<i>The way I wanted to be</i>

08:18.480 --> 08:20.680
<i>turned out to be ridiculous.</i>

08:21.720 --> 08:23.000
<i>It was at that moment</i>

08:24.040 --> 08:26.080
<i>that I met Xun.</i>

08:30.280 --> 08:31.760
How are the stars here,

08:31.840 --> 08:33.520
compared to those in the desert?

08:34.360 --> 08:35.640
Zhao.

08:35.720 --> 08:36.799
They're as beautiful.

08:45.560 --> 08:48.680
<i>That was the first time he called my name.</i>

08:49.200 --> 08:50.440
<i>And just because of that,</i>

08:50.960 --> 08:54.040
<i>I finally felt</i>
<i>that the Capital had accepted me.</i>

08:54.120 --> 08:57.960
<i>Because someone here cared for me,</i>
<i>thought of me, and cherished me.</i>

08:59.200 --> 09:02.680
<i>Shortly after that,</i>
<i>Xun went to Yunzhong to propose.</i>

09:09.360 --> 09:10.600
Zhao.

09:11.440 --> 09:12.640
The desert scenery

09:13.160 --> 09:14.400
is far grander than that of the Capital.

09:15.000 --> 09:16.360
It's been three years.

09:16.440 --> 09:17.760
You must have missed your hometown.

09:19.240 --> 09:20.360
Not really.

09:21.760 --> 09:23.840
Sand always swirls across the sky here.

09:24.840 --> 09:26.120
Seeing it too often

09:27.240 --> 09:28.200
makes it dull instead.

09:33.160 --> 09:35.040
You there, listen up!

09:35.120 --> 09:37.560
Give me all the valuables!

09:38.560 --> 09:40.560
Your Highness, we're ambushed.

09:45.800 --> 09:49.040
Be wise enough, and I'll let you live!

09:49.120 --> 09:52.160
Otherwise, I'll kill you all!

10:07.960 --> 10:09.560
Young man, who are you?

10:16.600 --> 10:18.320
FU JIU, CHU FAMILY'S RETAINER

10:18.400 --> 10:19.760
How noisy.

10:24.920 --> 10:26.880
Lads, go get him.

10:50.480 --> 10:51.560
Your Highness,

10:51.640 --> 10:53.280
I've never seen such fierce swordsmanship.

10:54.200 --> 10:55.560
Every strike is fatal.

11:04.720 --> 11:05.640
I'm Fu Jiu,

11:06.280 --> 11:07.440
working for General Chu.

11:08.440 --> 11:10.760
He sent me to kill the bandits.

11:14.080 --> 11:15.120
Help me, my lord!

11:16.360 --> 11:17.360
Stay back!

11:18.120 --> 11:19.760
Or I'll kill her.

11:36.240 --> 11:37.200
Are you insane?

11:37.280 --> 11:38.440
She's innocent.

11:47.400 --> 11:48.600
Foolish.

11:59.520 --> 12:00.840
Her bracelet

12:00.920 --> 12:03.520
and the chief's necklace
belong to the same set.

12:03.600 --> 12:04.680
Rare in the market.

12:05.320 --> 12:07.520
Just now, she deliberately
rushed out from behind.

12:08.520 --> 12:10.240
So, the bandit managed to seize her.

12:11.880 --> 12:14.600
Xun, before departure,

12:14.680 --> 12:17.360
did you verify the identity
of your attendants?

12:17.440 --> 12:18.880
The other day,

12:18.960 --> 12:21.480
I did notice some unfamiliar servants.

12:23.040 --> 12:24.160
But in a hurry,

12:24.680 --> 12:25.800
I didn't scrutinize.

12:29.440 --> 12:30.920
You were careless.

12:47.080 --> 12:49.120
YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

12:50.000 --> 12:52.680
I've sincerely come here
to propose to your daughter.

12:52.760 --> 12:54.240
Betrothal gifts are ready.

12:54.320 --> 12:55.440
Here is the list.

12:56.160 --> 12:57.880
Please review it.

13:00.440 --> 13:02.560
My daughter

13:03.400 --> 13:04.920
isn't good enough for a noble gentleman.

13:06.280 --> 13:07.120
Your Highness,

13:07.640 --> 13:09.400
I suggest you go back.

13:09.920 --> 13:13.280
Father, Xun and I love each other.

13:13.360 --> 13:14.600
What's wrong with his origin?

13:15.200 --> 13:16.360
If I can't marry him,

13:16.960 --> 13:17.840
why did you marry my mother,

13:17.920 --> 13:19.760
a noble young lady from far away?

13:19.840 --> 13:21.440
She stayed with you
and wasted her life here.

13:21.520 --> 13:22.360
Shut up.

13:22.960 --> 13:24.120
Your mother…

13:24.640 --> 13:25.800
You have no right to judge.

13:25.880 --> 13:27.360
Then don't interfere with mine!

13:28.200 --> 13:31.280
Zhao, don't be angry with General Chu.

13:33.880 --> 13:35.000
General Chu,

13:35.080 --> 13:37.520
I know what you're worried about.

13:38.120 --> 13:39.480
Anyone who commands

13:40.000 --> 13:42.120
200,000 frontier troops

13:42.200 --> 13:44.360
would be worried that I pursued Zhao

13:44.440 --> 13:45.720
with ulterior motives.

13:45.800 --> 13:47.280
But I do not

13:47.800 --> 13:49.200
have any other motives.

13:49.720 --> 13:50.680
I only have a true heart.

13:52.640 --> 13:54.760
What's the value

13:56.040 --> 13:57.480
of a so-called true heart?

14:02.520 --> 14:03.720
Five years ago,

14:04.600 --> 14:06.040
I went to the Capital as a hostage.

14:07.200 --> 14:09.000
His Majesty gave me a mansion.

14:09.080 --> 14:10.800
To me,

14:11.800 --> 14:13.080
that is a reward

14:13.760 --> 14:15.000
as well as a shackle.

14:15.600 --> 14:16.960
I'm kept alive

14:17.480 --> 14:19.240
to counterbalance Xiaonan Prefecture.

14:20.080 --> 14:21.440
My father sent me there

14:22.200 --> 14:23.680
to protect our clan.

14:25.280 --> 14:26.720
I have no say in any of these.

14:27.560 --> 14:29.160
General Chu, you're right.

14:29.800 --> 14:32.040
No one would care about my heart.

14:34.040 --> 14:35.440
All these years,

14:35.960 --> 14:39.040
rumors in the Capital have never ceased.

14:39.960 --> 14:42.600
I'm used to tolerating them
and not arguing back.

14:43.800 --> 14:44.680
But it's different now.

14:47.400 --> 14:48.560
I love Zhao.

14:48.640 --> 14:51.440
I don't want my love for her
to be misunderstood.

14:53.120 --> 14:54.400
If I ever betray you,

14:57.840 --> 14:59.600
you could kill me now.

15:10.280 --> 15:11.440
Who are you trying to embarrass?

15:12.040 --> 15:14.160
Heir to the Lord of Xiaonan or my husband?

15:14.760 --> 15:16.680
If he really killed himself to prove it,

15:16.760 --> 15:17.640
would you be satisfied?

15:17.720 --> 15:19.600
We'll stop here on this matter!

15:23.560 --> 15:24.800
Your Highness,

15:26.240 --> 15:27.800
I suggest you go back.

15:31.760 --> 15:32.760
But General…

15:47.480 --> 15:48.640
General.

15:49.520 --> 15:50.360
Zhao!

16:11.520 --> 16:12.360
Where's my father?

16:13.520 --> 16:15.480
He's on a mission.
He sent me to see you off.

16:19.440 --> 16:20.280
No need.

16:21.360 --> 16:22.600
You're like him.

16:22.680 --> 16:23.680
You both despise Xun.

16:24.280 --> 16:25.800
When you don't mean it,

16:25.880 --> 16:27.160
you don't need to pretend.

16:30.280 --> 16:31.400
Whatever you think.

16:32.280 --> 16:34.400
But if one day you regret it,

16:34.480 --> 16:35.840
come back anytime.

16:41.400 --> 16:43.000
Master said that.

16:44.920 --> 16:47.880
Then please take my message
to General Chu.

16:50.640 --> 16:51.920
I won't regret it.

16:53.000 --> 16:54.800
Nor will I come back here.

17:11.319 --> 17:12.760
<i>That farewell to my father</i>

17:14.040 --> 17:15.520
<i>was forever.</i>

17:25.800 --> 17:28.240
THE 19TH YEAR OF TIANSHU

17:28.960 --> 17:30.520
<i>After I returned to the Capital,</i>

17:31.480 --> 17:33.320
<i>I never stopped missing my father.</i>

17:34.520 --> 17:36.440
<i>It's not that he doesn't love me.</i>

17:36.520 --> 17:38.360
<i>He's just not good at showing his love.</i>

17:39.480 --> 17:42.120
<i>So, I often made his favorite jujube cakes</i>

17:42.200 --> 17:44.720
<i>and had them sent monthly to Yunzhong.</i>

17:59.400 --> 18:02.280
Hang the red silk
and your wish will come true.

18:04.760 --> 18:08.120
<i>But still, Father didn't approve</i>
<i>of this marriage.</i>

18:08.800 --> 18:10.200
<i>Two years later,</i>

18:10.280 --> 18:12.440
<i>Xiao Xun begged his father</i>
<i>to submit a memorial.</i>

18:12.520 --> 18:14.520
<i>They renounced their fief and troops.</i>

18:14.600 --> 18:16.320
<i>Finally, His Majesty granted the marriage.</i>

18:22.280 --> 18:24.280
I just made a divination for you.

18:24.360 --> 18:26.560
A pair of phoenixes fly
and flap their feathers.

18:26.640 --> 18:27.600
Great luck.

18:28.200 --> 18:29.840
The eighth day of next month,
25 days from now,

18:29.920 --> 18:31.200
will be a rare lucky day.

18:31.280 --> 18:33.160
Everything will go smoothly.

18:35.880 --> 18:39.080
And anyway,
even if His Highness dared to hurt you,

18:39.160 --> 18:41.040
General Chu wouldn't let that happen.

18:41.880 --> 18:42.880
Look.

18:49.960 --> 18:52.480
Fu Jiu said he was sent
to deliver your dowry.

18:52.560 --> 18:53.760
But we all know

18:53.840 --> 18:56.880
your father sent him to stand up for you.

19:17.240 --> 19:19.080
<i>Twenty five days later, it was</i>
<i>the 8th day of the 8th month,</i>

19:19.160 --> 19:20.000
<i>the 19th year of Tianshu.</i>

19:20.640 --> 19:22.840
<i>On my wedding night with Xiao Xun,</i>

19:22.920 --> 19:24.920
<i>rebels invaded the Capital.</i>

19:25.000 --> 19:28.160
<i>The whole city was ravaged by war.</i>

19:31.360 --> 19:32.200
What happened?

19:32.280 --> 19:34.000
I heard the Third Prince
killed the Crown Prince

19:34.080 --> 19:35.560
and led a rebellion.

19:39.880 --> 19:40.880
Where's Xun?

19:40.960 --> 19:42.800
His Highness orders your protection.

19:42.880 --> 19:45.200
Please stay in the Chu Mansion.

19:47.960 --> 19:50.040
By order, you should stay here.

20:01.120 --> 20:03.680
<i>Xun killed the Third Prince</i>

20:05.200 --> 20:07.200
<i>and ended this rebellion.</i>

20:08.160 --> 20:10.000
An urgent message!

20:10.080 --> 20:11.800
The Emperor passed away!

20:11.880 --> 20:14.160
The Third Prince rebelled
and was executed!

20:14.240 --> 20:17.080
The Crown Prince
and the eldest imperial grandson died!

20:17.640 --> 20:20.080
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

20:20.160 --> 20:22.000
suppressed the rebellion!

20:22.080 --> 20:25.000
He'll take the throne,
by the late emperor's will!

20:31.280 --> 20:34.200
<i>The Crown Prince died.</i>
<i>The Third Prince was executed.</i>

20:35.200 --> 20:38.040
<i>The imperial grandson Xiao Yu</i>
<i>died in the mutiny.</i>

20:38.120 --> 20:39.200
<i>The late emperor died.</i>

20:39.800 --> 20:43.240
<i>In the royal clan,</i>
<i>only Xiao Xun was left for the throne.</i>

20:44.240 --> 20:47.320
<i>Three days later, he ascended the throne</i>

20:47.400 --> 20:49.320
<i>and began his reign of the Anping era.</i>

20:50.120 --> 20:52.800
<i>This bloody fight for the throne</i>
<i>came to an end.</i>

20:52.880 --> 20:56.080
<i>It was known as the Anping Rebellion.</i>

21:11.640 --> 21:13.680
TAIJI HALL

21:14.280 --> 21:15.640
Your Majesty,

21:15.720 --> 21:17.560
may you have longevity

21:17.640 --> 21:19.600
and a prosperous reign!

21:19.680 --> 21:21.840
Your Majesty,

21:21.920 --> 21:23.280
may you have longevity

21:23.360 --> 21:25.000
and a prosperous reign!

21:27.680 --> 21:29.240
Your Majesty,

21:29.320 --> 21:31.200
may you have longevity

21:31.280 --> 21:33.400
and a prosperous reign!

21:34.240 --> 21:35.920
Your Majesty,

21:36.000 --> 21:37.720
may you have longevity

21:37.800 --> 21:40.000
and a prosperous reign!

21:40.720 --> 21:44.280
Your Majesty, may you have longevity

21:44.360 --> 21:46.480
and a prosperous reign!

21:48.840 --> 21:50.360
I returned without a command.

21:50.440 --> 21:51.680
I know I'm guilty.

21:51.760 --> 21:53.760
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

21:55.440 --> 21:56.960
Don't say that, Father-in-law.

21:57.480 --> 21:58.800
You traveled day and night.

21:58.880 --> 22:00.680
Your love for your daughter

22:00.760 --> 22:02.320
is as clear as day.

22:02.400 --> 22:04.320
I… I'm quite gratified.

22:05.200 --> 22:06.640
I won't blame you.

22:06.720 --> 22:08.800
You once asked me

22:08.880 --> 22:12.120
about the value of my true heart.

22:12.200 --> 22:14.320
I was once a hostage.

22:14.400 --> 22:16.600
I know the pain of family separation.

22:16.680 --> 22:20.880
For Zhao,
I request that you stay in the Capital.

22:21.720 --> 22:25.280
As for the border,
I'll have everything arranged.

22:27.040 --> 22:30.080
I wonder if you will agree to my request.

22:36.560 --> 22:37.800
Your Majesty,

22:39.040 --> 22:40.680
I've devoted my life to ending the war.

22:41.480 --> 22:42.680
I have only one daughter.

22:43.320 --> 22:46.440
I treasure her more than my own life.

22:48.840 --> 22:52.640
Your Majesty,
please take good care of my daughter.

22:52.720 --> 22:54.960
My 200,000 frontier troops

22:55.480 --> 22:58.240
will also devote themselves to the good

22:59.240 --> 23:01.200
of our nation.

23:03.040 --> 23:04.160
Of course.

23:32.160 --> 23:33.360
Jiu,

23:35.320 --> 23:38.160
from this day on,
you'll stay here to protect Zhao.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.440
This is an order.

24:02.480 --> 24:04.640
VIRTUE OVER ALL LANDS

24:04.720 --> 24:06.040
<i>After Xun's enthronement,</i>

24:06.680 --> 24:08.600
<i>Father hurried back to Yunzhong.</i>

24:09.560 --> 24:10.920
<i>He didn't attend my wedding.</i>

24:12.160 --> 24:16.320
<i>My marriage with Xun</i>
<i>went against Father's will after all.</i>

24:16.400 --> 24:19.080
Take a look. Satisfied?

24:23.880 --> 24:26.120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

24:30.760 --> 24:34.040
Yesterday,
you suggested lower textile taxes.

24:34.120 --> 24:35.920
Can you explain that more clearly?

24:37.440 --> 24:38.920
As a thank-you for what I just did.

24:40.240 --> 24:42.640
<i>Xun respected and loved me.</i>

24:42.720 --> 24:44.280
<i>An emperor like him</i>

24:44.360 --> 24:46.440
<i>often talked to me about state affairs.</i>

24:46.960 --> 24:49.400
<i>And he often carried out my suggestions</i>

24:49.480 --> 24:51.520
<i>to pacify the people.</i>

24:52.400 --> 24:55.720
<i>People praised him,</i>
<i>and their lives improved.</i>

24:55.800 --> 24:59.800
<i>I thought Father</i>
<i>might feel a little relieved.</i>

25:08.080 --> 25:09.520
<i>Every month, I wrote a letter to Father.</i>

25:09.600 --> 25:10.440
ALL GOOD IN THE PALACE

25:10.520 --> 25:11.960
<i>Yet he never wrote back.</i>

25:13.160 --> 25:15.080
<i>I wanted these letters of reassurance</i>

25:15.840 --> 25:18.000
<i>to soothe Father's worries.</i>

25:21.840 --> 25:25.520
<i>The Spring Equinox in the third year</i>
<i>of Anping was my 22nd birthday.</i>

25:26.400 --> 25:28.160
<i>Because I missed Father too much,</i>

25:28.240 --> 25:30.880
<i>Xun allowed me</i>
<i>to invite Father for my birthday</i>

25:30.960 --> 25:33.640
<i>and promised he'd be welcomed</i>
<i>as the Empress's father</i>

25:33.720 --> 25:35.560
<i>and get a corresponding residence.</i>

25:36.200 --> 25:37.880
<i>I was nervous.</i>

25:37.960 --> 25:39.720
<i>I was also eagerly anticipating it.</i>

25:39.800 --> 25:40.840
VIRTUE OVER ALL LANDS

25:42.040 --> 25:43.200
Soldiers, disarm.

25:44.520 --> 25:46.920
General, will we really disarm?

25:47.000 --> 25:48.800
It's Zhao's birthday.

25:50.440 --> 25:51.360
Let's do it.

25:59.360 --> 26:01.840
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

26:01.920 --> 26:03.920
is summoned for an audience!

26:37.160 --> 26:41.000
Go, Zhao.
Later, I have a surprise for you.

26:44.000 --> 26:45.440
Thank you, Your Majesty.

26:46.520 --> 26:49.920
Greetings, Your Majesty.

26:55.360 --> 26:56.600
Father.

27:01.240 --> 27:02.960
You had a long trip, General.

27:05.520 --> 27:06.600
Read the edict.

27:07.320 --> 27:10.960
Edict for Chu Ling, the Guard General!

27:14.360 --> 27:17.520
Upon investigation,
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

27:18.040 --> 27:21.560
coerced the Emperor
and colluded with northern enemies.

27:22.080 --> 27:23.600
His brother Chu Lan

27:24.480 --> 27:27.920
poisoned the eldest imperial grandson
in the first year of Anping.

27:28.520 --> 27:32.120
The Chu clan shall be executed.

27:33.680 --> 27:34.920
Impossible!

27:35.560 --> 27:38.200
My father has always been loyal
without any improper desires.

27:38.280 --> 27:39.960
My uncle has been timid.

27:40.040 --> 27:42.240
In no way would he poison
the imperial grandson.

27:42.920 --> 27:43.760
You…

27:43.840 --> 27:45.040
You must be mistaken.

27:45.120 --> 27:47.080
Your Majesty. He is mistaken.

27:47.160 --> 27:49.200
Your Majesty, the other day,

27:49.280 --> 27:51.600
you said you'd give my father a mansion.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.960
Zhao,

27:53.960 --> 27:56.880
colluding with northern enemies
is a grave crime.

27:57.480 --> 27:59.480
Your father did something foolish.

27:59.560 --> 28:01.480
Even if you're the Empress,

28:02.000 --> 28:06.720
I have to answer
to all the people of my nation.

28:07.840 --> 28:09.360
In the first year of Anping,

28:09.440 --> 28:10.840
Your Majesty ascended the throne.

28:10.920 --> 28:12.680
Northern enemies
invaded Yunzhong at night.

28:12.760 --> 28:15.920
My father led 200,000 frontier troops
to defend the town without retreating!

28:16.520 --> 28:18.440
Now, he's accused
of colluding with enemies!

28:18.520 --> 28:19.600
Who?

28:20.200 --> 28:21.400
Who accused him?

28:21.480 --> 28:23.160
Who offered the evidence?

28:23.240 --> 28:25.200
The truth must be sorted out.

28:25.280 --> 28:26.880
Otherwise, it's a frame-up.

28:27.680 --> 28:31.120
The Empress is delirious
and spouting nonsense.

28:32.320 --> 28:33.160
Bring poisoned wine…

28:37.000 --> 28:38.200
and execute the Empress's father.

28:42.480 --> 28:44.840
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

28:45.360 --> 28:47.960
Your Majesty. My father is innocent.

28:48.040 --> 28:49.480
He's innocent!

28:49.560 --> 28:51.960
Your Majesty, my father is innocent.

28:52.040 --> 28:53.320
He's innocent!

28:53.400 --> 28:54.880
I said, execute him!

28:56.200 --> 28:57.680
Xun! Xun!

28:59.880 --> 29:01.120
Xun.

29:03.280 --> 29:05.040
Xun. Xun.

29:05.640 --> 29:06.880
My father is innocent.

29:06.960 --> 29:08.520
Xun.

29:09.040 --> 29:10.840
Please spare my father. Xun.

29:22.080 --> 29:23.040
Changrong!

29:46.680 --> 29:48.760
You tread on the lives of frontier troops

29:48.840 --> 29:51.360
to appease your people
and secure your nation!

29:52.040 --> 29:55.840
So, this turns out to be your true heart.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.480
I've never dared to forget

29:58.280 --> 30:00.800
what you said on my enthronement day.

30:01.400 --> 30:02.400
Rest assured.

30:02.480 --> 30:04.560
Your 200,000 frontier troops

30:04.640 --> 30:06.120
will still devote themselves

30:06.200 --> 30:08.640
to my nation and me.

30:09.400 --> 30:12.240
General Chu Ling pulled out his blade
in front of His Majesty,

30:12.760 --> 30:14.000
intending to rebel.

30:14.080 --> 30:14.960
Execute him now!

30:24.280 --> 30:26.200
Father! Father!

30:26.280 --> 30:27.400
Father.

30:28.360 --> 30:29.280
Are you all right?

30:29.800 --> 30:31.720
Father. Sorry, Father.

30:33.160 --> 30:36.240
Father. Father. Sorry.

30:37.040 --> 30:38.920
I'm sorry, Father.

30:40.200 --> 30:41.200
I'm sorry.

30:41.720 --> 30:44.240
It's my fault. Father.

30:44.320 --> 30:46.800
Father, I'm sorry.

31:00.800 --> 31:02.920
-Xiao Xun, what do you want?
-Zhao.

31:03.000 --> 31:04.360
What are you going to do?

31:04.440 --> 31:06.280
-No.
-This is my surprise for you.

31:06.360 --> 31:08.120
No! No!

31:08.720 --> 31:10.240
Xiao Xun, let go of my father.

31:10.320 --> 31:12.280
No! No!

31:22.840 --> 31:26.520
The Empress shall be given poisoned wine

31:26.600 --> 31:29.280
for the sake of her filial devotion.

31:48.120 --> 31:49.560
I know you hate me.

31:52.280 --> 31:53.600
But you know that.

31:54.280 --> 31:55.240
In this case,

31:56.320 --> 31:58.320
if I hadn't convicted Chu Ling,

31:58.960 --> 32:01.440
how could I bring his frontier troops
under my control?

32:03.280 --> 32:05.720
Now, the whole nation is within my grasp,

32:06.720 --> 32:09.040
except for your father's troops!

32:09.120 --> 32:11.560
How can I secure this empire?

32:12.160 --> 32:13.480
Everyone in this nation says

32:14.680 --> 32:17.080
I wouldn't have succeeded
without a woman's help.

32:17.920 --> 32:21.240
They never see my hard reforms
over the past three years!

32:21.320 --> 32:22.960
They never see my diligent governance!

32:23.040 --> 32:25.080
They never see anything I've done!

32:25.160 --> 32:27.720
They can only see your father

32:27.800 --> 32:29.320
and his 200,000 frontier troops!

32:31.560 --> 32:32.760
But you said

32:34.520 --> 32:35.960
you didn't care.

32:36.760 --> 32:38.200
How could I not care?

32:39.400 --> 32:41.040
These 200,000 frontier troops

32:42.040 --> 32:43.760
were like a festering sore.

32:43.840 --> 32:44.960
Because of them,

32:45.040 --> 32:47.480
I couldn't sleep all night,
tormented by pain.

32:59.240 --> 33:00.960
I know you want to ask me

33:03.120 --> 33:05.200
why I did all this on your birthday.

33:06.920 --> 33:08.480
Because Zhao…

33:08.560 --> 33:10.520
Without your letter,

33:11.320 --> 33:12.600
he wouldn't have come back

33:13.960 --> 33:15.680
or disarmed.

33:16.440 --> 33:17.720
I wouldn't have managed

33:18.400 --> 33:19.760
to accuse him of rebelling

33:20.440 --> 33:22.480
even without his soldiers.

33:24.160 --> 33:27.680
Zhao, you're so clever.

33:28.520 --> 33:31.840
How could you not know

33:32.880 --> 33:36.880
your letter would make him
let down his guard?

33:37.480 --> 33:40.760
The 17th day of next month
will be your 22nd birthday.

33:40.840 --> 33:43.400
I drafted a decree to summon your father.

33:43.480 --> 33:45.080
As the Empress's father,

33:45.600 --> 33:47.280
he'll have a residence
in the imperial city.

33:48.400 --> 33:50.600
Write a letter to tell him about this.

33:51.680 --> 33:52.640
Why?

33:52.720 --> 33:55.160
Why did you do this to my clan?

33:55.240 --> 33:57.240
Why did you do this to me?

33:57.320 --> 33:59.240
Why?

34:14.400 --> 34:17.400
Actually, whether he did or didn't disarm,

34:18.800 --> 34:19.840
he'd end up the same.

34:22.800 --> 34:24.880
After I sent him away
on my enthronement day,

34:26.159 --> 34:27.560
I secretly had my men

34:27.639 --> 34:30.600
poison the jujube cakes
you sent to Yunzhong.

34:31.120 --> 34:34.199
From the Capital to Yunzhong,

34:34.280 --> 34:35.639
they were delivered monthly.

34:35.719 --> 34:37.199
CHU MANSION

34:37.880 --> 34:39.560
<i>Chu Ling would be killed anyway.</i>

34:40.280 --> 34:42.000
<i>Not only by my blade,</i>

34:42.960 --> 34:44.920
<i>but also by his daughter's love.</i>

35:10.880 --> 35:13.760
I'm going to kill you.

35:18.400 --> 35:19.920
Listen, Zhao.

35:21.680 --> 35:23.240
"In the third year of Anping,

35:25.200 --> 35:26.840
Chu clan was exterminated.

35:26.920 --> 35:28.920
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

35:30.000 --> 35:33.040
was guilty of treason and was executed.

35:33.920 --> 35:37.480
His daughter was so grieved

35:38.560 --> 35:40.200
that she hanged herself."

35:52.600 --> 35:54.080
<i>Father is right.</i>

35:54.600 --> 35:56.800
<i>The Capital is a devouring cage.</i>

35:57.560 --> 36:00.040
<i>I wrongly believed his fake gentleness.</i>

36:00.560 --> 36:03.360
<i>I wrongly believed his fake loyalty.</i>

36:03.440 --> 36:04.720
<i>And I wrongly believed</i>

36:05.480 --> 36:07.440
<i>his insatiable ambition.</i>

36:28.880 --> 36:30.360
<i>It was him…</i>

37:07.400 --> 37:09.880
<i>I once had many choices in this life.</i>

37:11.360 --> 37:13.760
<i>But I was so willful and ignorant.</i>

37:14.800 --> 37:16.800
<i>I made a wrong choice every time.</i>

37:18.480 --> 37:20.640
<i>I got my father killed.</i>

37:22.000 --> 37:23.920
<i>I ruined my whole clan.</i>

37:25.200 --> 37:26.440
<i>Father!</i>

37:29.280 --> 37:31.360
<i>I got myself killed too.</i>

37:43.680 --> 37:44.560
VOID AND BEING AS ONE

38:01.000 --> 38:04.400
<i>A pair of phoenixes fly</i>
<i>and flap their feathers.</i>

38:04.480 --> 38:05.440
<i>Great luck.</i>

38:07.920 --> 38:09.640
THE 19TH YEAR OF TIANSHU

38:23.000 --> 38:24.920
HEART AT PEACE, LET THINGS BE

38:25.000 --> 38:26.400
<i>Not to mention</i>
<i>the glorious dress and coronet,</i>

38:26.480 --> 38:28.120
<i>you even deserve the 12 ornaments</i>
<i>of imperial Robes.</i>

38:28.640 --> 38:30.160
<i>But I do not have any other motives.</i>

38:30.240 --> 38:31.160
<i>I only have a true heart.</i>

38:31.240 --> 38:32.080
<i>I love Zhao.</i>

38:32.160 --> 38:34.600
<i>I don't want my love for her</i>
<i>to be misunderstood.</i>

38:49.440 --> 38:50.920
Miss.

38:51.560 --> 38:53.200
What year is it now?

38:53.280 --> 38:55.560
You're so rude. Let go of me.

38:56.080 --> 38:58.720
It's the 14th day of the seventh month,
the 19th year of Tianshu!

38:59.480 --> 39:02.040
-Miss, don't do this. Let go.
-The 19th year of Tianshu?

39:02.120 --> 39:03.360
Don't you dare bully her!

39:03.440 --> 39:04.560
Don't be ridiculous.

39:04.640 --> 39:06.480
Just now, she almost hurt my hand.

39:07.680 --> 39:08.680
-Miss.
-Odd.

39:08.760 --> 39:09.720
Are you fine?

39:11.080 --> 39:12.520
You're real.

39:13.600 --> 39:16.040
I just went away to fetch red silk.

39:16.120 --> 39:17.400
Miss, what happened to you?

39:22.080 --> 39:23.880
I'm still alive.

39:23.960 --> 39:25.280
Did you lose your mind,

39:25.960 --> 39:28.120
or are you possessed?

39:28.640 --> 39:30.840
Shall I take you back
and wash you with pomelo leaves?

39:33.120 --> 39:33.960
I'll go get His Highness.

39:34.040 --> 39:35.040
Zhao.

39:48.480 --> 39:49.320
<i>Now I'm the Emperor.</i>

39:49.400 --> 39:51.960
<i>I'll never make you</i>
<i>shed tears because of farewells.</i>

39:52.040 --> 39:53.280
<i>You only need to dress yourself up</i>

39:53.360 --> 39:55.200
<i>and make yourself beautiful.</i>

40:06.440 --> 40:07.760
What's wrong, Zhao?

40:08.520 --> 40:09.440
Why are you crying?

40:09.520 --> 40:11.200
I'm going to kill you!

40:11.280 --> 40:12.560
You killed my father.

40:12.640 --> 40:13.480
I'll kill you!

40:14.080 --> 40:15.080
Miss.

40:15.160 --> 40:16.160
I'll kill you.

40:16.240 --> 40:17.720
I will.

40:29.840 --> 40:32.400
Thank you, Fu Jiu, for the dowry.

40:32.480 --> 40:36.160
Recently,
she has been nervous about the wedding.

40:36.240 --> 40:37.080
So…

40:37.680 --> 40:40.200
The dowry's been delivered. I'll leave.

40:57.560 --> 41:00.920
Today, Zhao acted strangely toward me.

41:01.520 --> 41:03.600
What on earth happened

41:04.840 --> 41:06.480
that changed her like that?

41:07.080 --> 41:09.720
The bell in Sanqing Temple
accidentally fell.

41:09.800 --> 41:10.960
Was she scared then?

41:11.560 --> 41:12.600
No.

41:14.280 --> 41:15.520
What she said was…

41:16.040 --> 41:17.280
You killed my father.

41:17.360 --> 41:18.880
I'm going to kill you!

41:20.320 --> 41:24.000
<i>I've never shown hostility</i>
<i>toward Chu Ling.</i>

41:24.080 --> 41:26.360
<i>Why did Zhao suddenly say</i>
<i>something like that?</i>

41:27.000 --> 41:30.320
<i>Could she have known my plan?</i>

41:52.120 --> 41:53.280
<i>How did this happen?</i>

41:57.120 --> 41:59.680
Miss, what happened to you?

42:00.280 --> 42:02.040
Shall I make a divination for you?

42:04.480 --> 42:05.360
Oh no.

42:05.440 --> 42:06.560
I'm not capable enough.

42:06.640 --> 42:08.200
I'll send for a Taoist master.

42:08.280 --> 42:09.240
Le,

42:12.320 --> 42:14.240
the 8th day of the 8th month this year

42:15.480 --> 42:17.680
is the wedding day for Xiao Xun and me.

42:17.760 --> 42:18.960
Right?

42:20.640 --> 42:22.560
His Majesty set this date.

42:23.880 --> 42:25.400
So, this is all real.

42:27.200 --> 42:28.240
Oh, you're bleeding.

42:28.320 --> 42:29.640
Don't you feel the pain?

42:32.480 --> 42:33.360
Yeah.

42:34.440 --> 42:36.000
When it hurts, it's real.

42:36.760 --> 42:38.040
It's real.

42:39.400 --> 42:40.240
Oh, dear.

42:40.320 --> 42:41.840
Don't scare me.

42:42.360 --> 42:44.480
What on earth happened?
Could you please tell me?

42:45.480 --> 42:47.240
Why are you crying again?

42:50.880 --> 42:53.960
Le, go make some calming soup for me.

42:57.360 --> 42:58.400
All right.

43:44.120 --> 43:45.320
Who are you?

43:45.400 --> 43:47.320
I am you.

43:48.440 --> 43:50.520
I'm all your resentment

43:50.600 --> 43:51.880
and all your hatred.

43:53.080 --> 43:55.720
I'm the blade you brought back
from the underworld.

43:56.520 --> 43:58.000
Just like the two sides

43:58.520 --> 44:00.720
of the robe.

44:02.640 --> 44:03.880
How did I come back to life?

44:03.960 --> 44:05.960
It's a heaven-sent opportunity.

44:06.040 --> 44:08.840
You can take your revenge.

44:13.080 --> 44:14.160
It's not easy

44:15.360 --> 44:16.880
to kill Xiao Xun.

44:17.520 --> 44:19.760
He's been scheming all the time,

44:19.840 --> 44:22.280
determined to be a decent gentleman.

44:22.360 --> 44:24.440
I have no chips to bring him down.

44:28.280 --> 44:32.400
My priority is to stay alive.

44:34.880 --> 44:37.240
Only when I'm alive can I save myself

44:37.320 --> 44:38.560
and save my father.

44:43.200 --> 44:44.440
Rest assured.

44:45.200 --> 44:48.080
I'll get revenge on Xiao Xun
in the same way

44:49.320 --> 44:51.880
he ruined the Chu family.

44:53.680 --> 45:00.520
I won't allow
even the slightest difference.

47:34.560 --> 47:36.880
Subtitle translation by:
